  "tells": [
    "Hold Thoughtseize for the opponent's most impactful card rather than using it preemptively",
    "Reanimate Archon of Cruelty when the opponent has multiple threats to maximize its combat trick",
    "Play Abhorrent Oculus when you need to dig for a specific reanimation target or answer",
    "Prioritize reanimating threats that can immediately impact the board state",
    "Common mistakes include overcommitting to the graveyard without protection, forgetting to track the opponent\u2019s hand for counters/removal, and missequencing mana for reanimation."
